title: SYNTHROTEK MOLEX POWER CABLE (12INCH)
description:
This 6-pin molex cable is used to connect Synthrotek's Deluxe Power and Noise Filtering Power Distribution Boards.

Use the Power Cable to connect the Deluxe Power to the Noise Filtering Power Distribution Board, or to connect two Distribution Boards together.

Use the Adapter Cable to connect Synthrotek's power to any other system. Â It has a male molex connector on one end and open wire on the other.
